{"tid":1417943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔主力掟屎/食物殘渣/其他污穢物","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:06:45.000Z","uid":275859,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e518e6b36cf7c676bb89908ea3bbf1fd1e5e324c","tid":1417943,"uid":275859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"之前見到有巴打出post話唔好掟磚怕形象唔好<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁點解唔主力向d狗掟屎/食物殘渣/其他污穢物？ 傷害無咁高之餘又帶有侮辱性。當然觸怒d狗係有危險性的，班狗可能會不惜一切衝過來攞命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嗱，我係話掟狗咋，千祈唔可以掟我地嘅官員/警察/其他駐港政要機構呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30091a5b49033af244c1d032a211445ae429a6c","tid":1417943,"uid":275859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75055ce13e4eb9032ee6840752f6d7d6a3599a88","tid":1417943,"uid":275859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d484353555c69dfdcb0d5c9cd812a8cb1681372c","tid":1417943,"uid":275859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713d16e6b972b40e618bfcb05ab511edc17b544f","tid":1417943,"uid":253174,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔掉狗糧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59e7c36016a6b010216e1e45fa39bd6268959ff","tid":1417943,"uid":288924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7d0a9c209652b8e4f24520675b2e43b49